{"tid":1430870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣撚入黎！文宣方向","createTime":"2019-08-08T00:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T07:53:02.000Z","uid":88507,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5d656c90ee92ab64941a26773542e829fe68d72b","tid":1430870,"uid":88507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:35:24.000Z","msg":"而家係鬥洗腦嘅年代<br />\n我哋唔可以咁被動見招拆招<br />\n咁樣落去時間一長就岌岌可危<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n我哋而家要主動出擊<br />\n好簡單一句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">讓我們拭目以待警察接下來的把戲，如何欺騙市民</span></span><br />\n必須不斷重複講<br />\n等非同溫層就算唔完全企喺我哋呢邊<br />\n都會思考黑警講嘢嘅真實性<br />\n<br />\n麻煩文宣手足整成一張圖post出去<br />\n可以加多句&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港警察，顛倒黑白</span></span>&rdquo;<br />\n連農牆都要大字報寫<br />\n化主動為被動"},{"pid":"66c50ac27fcfb34f156debe8501381584b55d86d","tid":1430870,"uid":88507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:39:28.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"108b8c266426e65ddb25108a281afa08769114f3","tid":1430870,"uid":88507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:39:40.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"284534494b6217e1d8c55c14efb95dab82cc80cf","tid":1430870,"uid":88507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:40:01.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"bf6ea4a2cf8bb2923cebe5eb1ae62a273bb6192b","tid":1430870,"uid":88507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:40:33.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"2a57656eadfd3a1ed1e6d915e52b864b73b69419","tid":1430870,"uid":88507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:40:46.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"10b653b1b0c91e3eefc6f1d824365fb1da5db231","tid":1430870,"uid":88507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:40:58.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"e12a6c3ba912576d557a36bd8297887f275d9f02","tid":1430870,"uid":88507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:41:09.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid"